  "detailed_description": "<h1>Wishlist Epic Auto Towers, a game from our son, a professional game developer!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>A pixel-art style puzzle platformer.<br>The level is passed when the hedgehogs collect all the apples.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 2 hedgehogs move left and right in sync.<br></li><li> The hedgehog cannot jump - use bounces from enemies or other game characters.<br></li><li> The moment one hedgehog is in the tube or lands on the boat, freely control the movement of the second hedgehog.<br></li><li> When one hedgehog encounters an obstacle, the second hedgehog can continue moving if its path is free.<br></li><li> 33 levels of increasing difficulty.<br></li><li> Look for a rational and easy way to complete them!</li></ul><br><br>      <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1716790/extras/a894c1d1d6d951a6514894728caa3524.poster.avif?t=1695479506\" width=416 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1716790/extras/a894c1d1d6d951a6514894728caa3524.webm?t=1695479506\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1716790/extras/a894c1d1d6d951a6514894728caa3524.mp4?t=1695479506\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "A pixel-art style puzzle platformer.<br>The level is passed when the hedgehogs collect all the apples.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 2 hedgehogs move left and right in sync.<br></li><li> The hedgehog cannot jump - use bounces from enemies or other game characters.<br></li><li> The moment one hedgehog is in the tube or lands on the boat, freely control the movement of the second hedgehog.<br></li><li> When one hedgehog encounters an obstacle, the second hedgehog can continue moving if its path is free.<br></li><li> 33 levels of increasing difficulty.<br></li><li> Look for a rational and easy way to complete them!</li></ul><br><br>      <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1716790/extras/a894c1d1d6d951a6514894728caa3524.poster.avif?t=1695479506\" width=416 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1716790/extras/a894c1d1d6d951a6514894728caa3524.webm?t=1695479506\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1716790/extras/a894c1d1d6d951a6514894728caa3524.mp4?t=1695479506\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
